    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a mechanically sound example of the E46 platform, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS timing. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with essential rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed cooling system to ensure thermal efficiency under load. While the exterior displays honest patina expected of a driver's car, the suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, providing the precise turn-in and analog feedback this chassis is heralded for. A well-sorted enthusiast vehicle ready for the B-roads.",
