    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Lexus RX 350 that perfectly balances luxury and reliability. Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 engine delivers a smooth, quiet ride with no mechanical issues, leaks, or warning lights. The transmission shifts effortlessly, and the suspension remains firm and responsive. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring parchment leather upholstery that remains soft and clean, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All power features, including the heated/ventilated seats, sunroof, and premium infotainment system, are fully operational. The exterior maintains a deep gloss, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, shallow door ding on the rear passenger side\u2014typical signs of careful daily use. This vehicle comes with a clean title, two sets of keys, and a comprehensive service history. It is a turn-key luxury SUV ready for its next owner.",
